00:31:21.659 --> 00:31:23.439
This is God's Word.

00:31:23.439 --> 00:31:24.439
This is authoritative.

00:31:24.439 --> 00:31:29.079
And you begin to think about all those things that have been invested in you.

00:31:29.079 --> 00:31:35.159
Someone said this, and I don't remember who it was, and so forgive me if you know who

00:31:35.159 --> 00:31:36.159
it is, that's fine.

00:31:36.159 --> 00:31:42.119
But someone said this, when I examined my own life of teaching and raising my children,

00:31:42.119 --> 00:31:49.119
it occurred to me that I was raising the parents of my grandchildren.

00:31:49.119 --> 00:31:53.720
Now, think about that for a moment.

00:31:53.720 --> 00:31:58.919
You're raising the parents of your grandchildren.

00:31:58.919 --> 00:32:03.759
I'm now in a place, Nova is two today, it's her birthday.

00:32:03.759 --> 00:32:09.559
And I didn't think about that 22 years ago when Juliana was born.

00:32:09.559 --> 00:32:14.959
But since I heard that or read that, I've thought about it often.

00:32:14.959 --> 00:32:20.720
How have, how have we, my wife and I, Holly and I, how have we engaged in teaching our

00:32:20.720 --> 00:32:31.119
children to have some Bible knowledge and something passed down to our grandchildren?

00:32:31.119 --> 00:32:32.279
Because that ought to be our desire.

00:32:32.279 --> 00:32:37.479
Listen, I'm so thankful that my kids are saved, but I want my grandkids to be saved.

00:32:37.479 --> 00:32:41.279
I want my grandkids to walk with God and live for God.

00:32:41.279 --> 00:32:44.160
I want them to serve God faithfully.

00:32:44.160 --> 00:32:50.279
I want them to use the talents that God would give them for God's honor and for God's glory.

00:32:50.279 --> 00:32:56.959
I don't want it to be a situation where someone along the line, 30, 40 years from now, knocks

00:32:56.959 --> 00:33:02.160
on one of my grandkids' door to talk to them about Jesus and they say, yeah, you know,

00:33:02.160 --> 00:33:10.399
my granddaddy, he was a, he was a pastor and, you know, no.

00:33:10.399 --> 00:33:13.160
And what we're teaching, we must examine.

00:33:13.160 --> 00:33:17.520
We live in a society that so many people get so caught up in teaching their kids how to

00:33:17.520 --> 00:33:22.559
do things that are temporal.

00:33:22.559 --> 00:33:26.800
I understand the temporal things and the fun things and all of that, but, you know, we

00:33:26.800 --> 00:33:34.339
need to engage in teaching a generation things that are eternal and making it a priority.

00:33:34.339 --> 00:33:43.199
And at some point saying, you know, this is eternal, this is temporal, this takes priority.

00:33:43.199 --> 00:33:45.720
They're going to get mad.

00:33:45.720 --> 00:33:49.080
They probably got mad when you made them eat broccoli.

00:33:49.080 --> 00:33:50.599
You know what I'm saying?

00:33:50.599 --> 00:33:55.119
And this evening, let's just do some, what are we doing, I think it was seven, seven

00:33:55.119 --> 00:33:57.880
kids stood up here tonight.

00:33:57.880 --> 00:34:02.639
There were ten in the junior high, senior high class that I taught this morning for

00:34:02.639 --> 00:34:05.639
Sunday school, ten.

00:34:05.639 --> 00:34:07.559
We have a little bit of a window.

00:34:07.559 --> 00:34:09.860
As a parent, you have a window.

00:34:09.860 --> 00:34:12.319
As a pastor, I have a window.

00:34:12.319 --> 00:34:15.479
As church members, we have a window.

00:34:16.239 --> 00:34:20.200
You say, well, none of them are my kids, but God's put you here.

00:34:20.200 --> 00:34:25.519
You can pray for them, you can have opportunities as God would provide you with them to be able

00:34:25.519 --> 00:34:29.040
to get involved and teach them.

00:34:29.040 --> 00:34:35.480
You know how good it is for the little kids to see the gray heads or the bald heads in

00:34:35.480 --> 00:34:37.480
church?

00:34:37.480 --> 00:34:39.119
Why?

00:34:39.119 --> 00:34:42.720
Because they're still living, they're still doing what they were teaching us.

00:34:42.720 --> 00:34:45.239
They're still here, they're still faithful.

00:34:45.279 --> 00:34:48.279
It makes a difference, it makes an impact.

00:34:48.279 --> 00:34:53.679
And so this evening, we see the example, we see those that engaged in it, but then let

00:34:53.679 --> 00:34:57.000
us examine, what are we teaching our children?

00:34:57.000 --> 00:34:59.899
What are we teaching a future generation?

00:34:59.899 --> 00:35:06.679
Because if we're saying to them, walk as you have been taught, then we better make sure

00:35:06.679 --> 00:35:10.760
we're teaching them how they should walk.

00:35:10.760 --> 00:35:11.760
Let's pray together.

00:35:11.760 --> 00:35:12.919
Father, we love you.

00:35:12.919 --> 00:35:14.359
Thank you so much for loving us.

00:35:14.359 --> 00:35:23.040
Thank you for what we've been able to hear and observe this evening with the junior church.

00:35:23.040 --> 00:35:28.639
I thank you for the families in our church, and God, I thank you for the opportunities

00:35:28.639 --> 00:35:35.359
that we have to be able to invest and train a future generation.

00:35:35.359 --> 00:35:42.600
God, I pray that you would help us tonight to see the importance of being involved, but

00:35:43.079 --> 00:35:48.679
I also pray that you would help us tonight to take a moment to just examine.

00:35:48.679 --> 00:35:52.279
Maybe there's some that have children still at home, and there's some things that need

00:35:52.279 --> 00:35:57.839
to be shifted, adjusted, refocused.

00:35:57.839 --> 00:36:03.200
Maybe for some of us, there's no more children at home, but Lord, there's children in our

00:36:03.200 --> 00:36:11.919
church that we can invest in and help be a positive, godly example to them.

00:36:11.919 --> 00:36:16.919
And I pray, Lord, that you'd help us to be purposed, intentional with regard to investing

00:36:16.919 --> 00:36:19.079
in a future generation.

00:36:19.079 --> 00:36:22.679
I pray that you would have your will and way in our hearts this evening.

00:36:22.679 --> 00:36:25.440
I pray that we'd be doers of the word, and we'll thank you for it.

00:36:25.440 --> 00:36:26.720
In Christ's name we pray.

00:36:26.720 --> 00:36:27.160
Would you stand?

